<section xmlns="http://xml.house.gov/schemas/uslm/1.0" style="-uslm-lc:I80" id="idede509ea-3a6e-11f1-addd-bbaf0b3f68e9" identifier="/us/usc/t7/s51"><num value="51">§ 51.</num><heading> Short title</heading><content>
<p style="-uslm-lc:I11" class="indent0">This chapter shall be known by the short title of “United States Cotton Standards Act.”</p>
</content><sourceCredit id="idede509eb-3a6e-11f1-addd-bbaf0b3f68e9">(<ref href="/us/act/1923-03-04/ch288/s1">Mar. 4, 1923, ch. 288, § 1</ref>, <ref href="/us/stat/42/1517">42 Stat. 1517</ref>.)</sourceCredit>
<notes type="uscNote" id="idede509ec-3a6e-11f1-addd-bbaf0b3f68e9">
<note style="-uslm-lc:I74" role="crossHeading" topic="statutoryNotes" id="idede509ed-3a6e-11f1-addd-bbaf0b3f68e9"><heading class="centered"><b>Statutory Notes and Related Subsidiaries</b></heading></note>
<note style="-uslm-lc:I74" topic="effectiveDate" id="idede509ee-3a6e-11f1-addd-bbaf0b3f68e9"><heading class="centered smallCaps">Effective Date</heading><p><ref href="/us/act/1923-03-04/ch288/s14">Act Mar. 4, 1923, ch. 288, § 14</ref>, <ref href="/us/stat/42/1520">42 Stat. 1520</ref>, provided: <quotedContent origin="/us/act/1923-03-04/ch288/s14">“That this Act [enacting this chapter] shall become effective on and after <date date="1923-08-01">August 1, 1923</date>.”</quotedContent>
</p>
</note>
</notes>
